title: JRE REVIEW of 1308 with Eddie Bravo
description:
Eddie Bravo is a jujitsu practitioner and stand up comedian. He loves his conspiracies and has known Joe for over 20 years and is one of his favorite people. It's always a good time having him on Joe's podcast making my time reviewing it that much more fun.
